# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 12. INTROSPECTION — explore the schema
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### List all query fields available
POST http://localhost:8000/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ __schema { queryType { fields { name description args { name type { name kind } } } } } }"
}

### Inspect Company type fields
POST http://localhost:8000/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ __type(name: \"Company\") { fields { name description type { name kind ofType { name kind } } } } }"
}
